  name: "Treacherous Plants"
  label: null
  type: null
  description: "The fey prankster can cause plants to distract nearby creatures. To\
    \ use this ability, the fey prankster attempts a Bluff check to create a distraction\
    \ to hide as a swift action or to feint against an adjacent opponent as a move\
    \ action, so long as the target is adjacent to plants. He gains a bonus on this\
    \ check equal to half his rogue level (minimum +1)."
